data.description:
This beautiful home will be available for occupancy starting December 15, 2023. This contemporary home is located in the family-friendly and highly desirable Hartley Hills sub-division. The home features an open-concept great room with generous and kitchen and dining spaces. Spacious primary suite and bedroom (or office/den) on the ground floor, with two additional bedrooms and bonus room (rec room) on second floor. Hardwood floors in common areas and carpeted in the bedrooms and bonus room. Attached two car garage with professional in-ground basketball goal. Located on a generous .75 acre lot, the home is part of well-maintained and quiet community. The home comes with zoned access to the newest schools: Kirkwood High and Middle schools.

Conveniently located off of exit 8 in Clarksville, this home is minutes away from exit 4 restaurants and shopping, only 25 minutes from Ft. Campbell, and 45 minutes from Nashville.

Open to short term leasing options. Tenant responsible for all utilities. Owner covers HOA fees (which includes trash disposal). Pets allowed on a case-by-case basis (with pet deposit).
